******************************************
1) instalar o node,js + npm

2) Instalar ionic 

    npm install -g ionic cordova

3) Criando projeto

    ionic start appteste blank

    templates:
        
        tabs : a simple 3 tab layout
        sidemenu: a layout with a swipable menu on the side
        blank: a bare starter with a single page
        super: starter project with over 14 ready to use page designs
        tutorial: a guided starter project

4) Teste browser (localhost:8100)
    ionic serve


5) Executando no device
    ionic cordova run android --device

    ionic cordova run android

    ionic build android


    Variaveis ambiente

        export ANDROID_HOME=/home/sergioweber/Android/Sdk

        export JAVA_HOME=/usr/lib/jvm/java-8-oracle

        export PATH=$PATH:/opt/android-studio/gradle/gradle-3.2/bin

        /home/sergioweber/Desenvolvimento/Ionic/appteste/platforms/android/build/outputs/apk/android-debug.apk
